## 🌟 3. Benefits of Prompt Engineering

| Benefit         | Description                                              |
|----------------|----------------------------------------------------------|
| 🎯 Precision     | Targeted, high-quality model outputs                    |
| ⚡ Efficiency     | Lower cost, faster responses                           |
| 🧠 Control       | Influence output tone, format, and reasoning            |
| 📈 Optimization | Improve model performance without retraining            |
| 🧪 Experimentation | Quickly prototype AI solutions                         |

